snippet.title: Snow Hunting | Season 8 Cinematic Trailer - Arena Breakout
snippet.description:
Seize the opportunity, or fall into the trap; become the hunter, or you will be the prey. Regardless of the outcome, the cold wind will carry away the noisy gunfire, and the heavy snow will bury the fallen warriors. Only the forests of Northridge will remember everything that has happened here.

Arena Breakout Season 8 launches in three days! 
The full experience will be available in Season 8 on iOS and Android! http://bit.ly/3Jel2aJ

#ArenaBreakoutS8 #FrozenFrontline #S8March20
